OL,5, A school board in Tennessee has banned 
OL,6, a Pulitzer prize-winning novel about   
OL,7, the Holocaust from being taught in its 
OL,8, classrooms.                            
OL,10,FBoard members voted in favour of       
OL,11,Fbanning the novel because it contained 
OL,12,Fswear words and a naked illustration.  
OL,14,FThe graphic novel Maus: A Survivor's   
OL,15,FTale depicts how the author's parents  
OL,16,Fsurvived Auschwitz during the          
OL,17,FHolocaust.                             
OL,19,FAuthor Art Spiegelman said he was      
OL,20,F"baffled" by the decision.             
